  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK417">
<l>piḻaittuṇarntum pētaimai collā riḻaittuṇarn</l>
<l>tīṇṭiya kēḷvi yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not even when they have imperfectly understood (a matter), will those men speak foolishly, who have profoundly studied and diligently listened (to instruction).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
